data.description: Experience the epitome of country living in this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home nestled on 4.91 acres of tranquility and convenience. Step into a spacious, newly updated kitchen with ample counter space and appliances, seamlessly flowing into the dining area and a generous living room bathed in natural light. Immerse yourself in the luxury of renovated bathrooms exuding elegant charm and comfort. The convenience of a dedicated laundry room with cabinetry adds to the allure. Outside, a 28x30 heated /cooled detached garage/workshop w/12x30 storage/expansion above, alongside two fenced areas perfect for your furry friends (presently used as Dog Boarding/Daycare business). A RV electrical hookup area available for the traveler and a storage building with electricity.  Swing set/Play area, sand pit, burn pit, apple & pear trees, blackberries, etc... all set against the backdrop of a great location. So much opportunity and fun for all to enjoy. Welcome to your next place to call HOME.
